# CADILLAC OPTIQ OWNER'S MANUAL

Thank you for choosing the Cadillac OPTIQ, Cadillac's compact electric luxury crossover.
rawText:
# CADILLAC OPTIQ OWNER'S MANUAL

Thank you for choosing the Cadillac OPTIQ, Cadillac's compact electric luxury crossover.

ocrText:
## INTRODUCTION

This manual provides essential information about your Cadillac OPTIQ. Read it thoroughly to familiarize yourself with your vehicle's features and operation.
rawText:
## INTRODUCTION

This manual provides essential information about your Cadillac OPTIQ. Read it thoroughly to familiarize yourself with your vehicle's features and operation.

ocrText:
## VEHICLE OVERVIEW

The Cadillac OPTIQ features premium electric performance in a compact crossover design, with advanced technology and luxury amenities.
rawText:
## VEHICLE OVERVIEW

The Cadillac OPTIQ features premium electric performance in a compact crossover design, with advanced technology and luxury amenities.

ocrText:
## CHARGING

Your Cadillac OPTIQ supports both AC and DC fast charging. Use the included Mobile Charging Cable for home charging or access public charging networks.
rawText:
## CHARGING

Your Cadillac OPTIQ supports both AC and DC fast charging. Use the included Mobile Charging Cable for home charging or access public charging networks.

ocrText:
## BATTERY SYSTEM

The OPTIQ features a 74 kWh battery providing up to 465 km of range (WLTP). The battery supports fast charging up to 150 kW.
